{"tid":925264,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)魔鬼末日 星際啟示錄","createTime":"2018-12-02T16:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T18:37:47.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3df7ba5bc9888624937851888633a98227311474","tid":925264,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6KqC%2BRlu7fUPzwnyrQUOUTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=20df2beb\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6KqC%2BRlu7fUPzwnyrQUOUTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b6e06672\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=6KqC%2BRlu7fUPzwnyrQUOUTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dbdb7def\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/73/End_of_days_ver5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F7%2F73%2FEnd_of_days_ver5.jpg&h=7c828510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.傑瑞柯是一名退休的警察，目前從事保全的工作。他和工作夥伴已經對工作感到厭倦。一次工作上槍擊的意外，慢慢牽引他走向一名年輕女子--克莉絲汀。克莉絲汀從小就經常在惡夢中見到一名男子，卻不知該名男子與自己的關係，直到一天，有一群神父闖進家門，意圖刺殺克莉絲汀，而傑瑞柯與夥伴即時搭救，她們才明白原來克莉絲汀是世界末日的關鍵......<br />\n<br />\n2.地球農作物因氣候轉變及枯萎病而經常失收，曾是美國國家航空暨太空總署的工程師和太空梭駕駛員的主角庫珀（Cooper）被迫成為農民以協助解決糧食危機。庫珀的10歲女兒墨菲（Murphy）發現其房間書架上的書本無故掉到地上，認為這是騷靈現象。不久後，一場沙塵暴在墨菲房間中留下二進制座標，二人驅車到達坐標位置後發現那是北美空防司令部（已成為美國國家航空暨太空總署的秘密基地）<br />\n<br />\n12 40AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6KqC%2BRlu7fUPzwnyrQUOUTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c50e66e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6KqC%2BRlu7fUPzwnyrQUOUTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=73371c5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ff9c95fb3700bc4421863763495275ee4e1dd0","tid":925264,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bc/Interstellar_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbc%2FInterstellar_film_poster.jpg&h=542b3efb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e7ad19806fd1bfa2ed7e05ef5af518b0a73c4db","tid":925264,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48bdfe23e21e14193b59f6bc76aa6f04ccd9dbc",